   title = "Priority Todos & Blocking Dependencies - 13 Active Items"
   description = "Critical priority tasks ordered by blocking dependencies. Includes Architecture Migration Phase 2, Master Plan Refactor, API Logging Fix, and DailyPlan Synchronization."
